Package io.cyborgcode.roa.api.core

Class ParametrizedEndpoint<T extends Enum<T>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.api.core.ParametrizedEndpoint<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Endpoint<T>
public class ParametrizedEndpoint<T extends Enum<T>> extends Object implements Endpoint<T>
A wrapper for Endpoint that allows adding query parameters, path parameters, and headers dynamically.

This class enables the creation of new endpoint instances with modified parameters while maintaining immutability.
